<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <Description>RaccoonLand storage-agnostic outbox abstractions: marker channels (IOutbox), the request-scoped IOutboxWriter for enqueueing messages, enqueue metadata, and the pending-message envelope. Per-channel storage configuration and the channel registry are intentionally left to the implementation (for example the SQL Server Commands module).</Description>
  </PropertyGroup>

</Project>
